"""decision_tree_ftmo_alpha.py - AUTO-GENERATED RL alpha (slot 16).

WHEN  : generated by ftmo_dt.train / export_tree on the frozen FTMO tree.
WHO   : decision-tree FTMO alpha (one tree, three surfaces).
WHY   : add a learned 3-class {+1,-1,0} setup detector to the RL pack without
        changing the locked observation (479 / 220). Reads only existing cached
        columns; derives scale-free features by plain arithmetic; evaluates a
        frozen if/else tree -- NO sklearn / pandas / TA-Lib in the hot loop.
WHERE : src/strategies/decision_tree_ftmo_alpha.py
HOW   : compute_signal(ctx) builds 48 features in FEATURES order from
        ctx.ind(col, tf), abstains (0) if ANY is non-finite (warm-up), else runs
        the frozen tree -> +1 / -1 / 0.
DEPENDS_ON : src/strategies/base.BaseStrategy ; ctx.ind(col, tf).
USED_BY    : src/strategies/alpha_pack.register_all (slot 16).
CHANGE_NOTES-IRAC : keep FEATURES order frozen; regenerate this whole file when
        the tree is retrained (never hand-edit the if/else).
"""
